{"id":371803,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/11/嘉兴日报评论员因发表反共反毛言论被开除/","date":"2014-11-23T05:46:43Z","modified":"2014-11-23T22:37:46Z","title":"【异闻观止】嘉兴日报评论员因发表反共反毛言论被开除","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/嘉兴日报.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-371813\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/嘉兴日报.png\" alt=\"嘉兴日报\" width=\"600\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/嘉兴日报.png 901w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/嘉兴日报-300x45.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>嘉兴日报：经报请集团研究决定，自即日起解除王垚烽与本报的劳动关系。对网友给予本报的关心，再致深谢。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>以下为王垚烽部分言论截图，图片来自网络：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkuwx7zf7j20jp0cugml.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-371808\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkuwx7zf7j20jp0cugml.jpg\" alt=\"63b790b5jw1emkuwx7zf7j20jp0cugml\" width=\"400\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkuwx7zf7j20jp0cugml.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkuwx7zf7j20jp0cugml-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkuwx7zf7j20jp0cugml-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/2014112311184795eea.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-371805\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/2014112311184795eea.jpg\" alt=\"2014112311184795eea\" width=\"400\" height=\"\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/2014112311184795eea.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/2014112311184795eea-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/02.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-371811\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/02.png\" alt=\"02\" width=\"375\" height=\"537\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/02.png 485w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/02-209x300.png 209w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/01.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-371810\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/01.png\" alt=\"01\" width=\"375\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/01.png 482w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/01-216x300.png 216w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutkotrzj20k00fiab1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-371809\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutkotrzj20k00fiab1.jpg\" alt=\"63b790b5jw1emkutkotrzj20k00fiab1\" width=\"400\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutkotrzj20k00fiab1.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutkotrzj20k00fiab1-300x232.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutywwq0j20bu0hswfb.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-371807\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutywwq0j20bu0hswfb.jpg\" alt=\"63b790b5jw1emkutywwq0j20bu0hswfb\" width=\"375\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutywwq0j20bu0hswfb.jpg 426w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/11/63b790b5jw1emkutywwq0j20bu0hswfb-199x300.jpg 199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a></p>\n<p>【早前报道】网友：党报嘉兴日报评论员王垚烽长期发布反共言论</p>\n<p>近日有网友称，浙江嘉兴日报社评论员王垚烽身为党报时事评论人员，却长期在微博发布反党反共反毛言论，被网友发现并公布后，王垚烽迅速删除了全部帖子。网友称，从网友部分截屏证据中可知，此人是肆无忌惮的反共反毛狂徒，甚至反对中国统一，支持占中，支持中国分裂，地方自治。</p>\n<p>学者司马南评论称：“将那些三观不正志在撞墙沉船的人，聘为党报评论员，让他们尽兴地在主流媒体上‘骂党黑国’这在中国早已经不是新闻。甭说嘉兴日报这类地方报纸，共青团中央机关报、省委机关报也不例外。”</p>\n<p>嘉兴日报今日上午10:30发表回应称：“感谢网友对本报的关心。本报已对王垚烽开展相关调查，将依规处理。”</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,20505],"tags":[13099,18804,23072,9375,21038,9553,26218]}